gbm_weights <- weightit(PA ~
                        age
                      + sex
                      + education
                      + employment
                      + relationship
                      + socialize
                      + sleep
                      + meddiagnosis
                      + mhseeking
                      + childtrauma
                      + adulttrauma,
                      data = cleandata,
                      method = "gbm",
                      estimand = "ATC",
                      trim.at = 0.99,
                      distribution = "bernoulli")
Warning: Missing values are present in the covariates. See ?WeightIt::method_gbm for information on how these are handled.
Warning: No stop.method was provided. Using "es.mean".
